list.name: Commit
list.query: SELECT * FROM events WHERE event = 'UI_COMMIT_COMPLETED' AND $timeFilter

panels.description: Overall pps of IPv6 and IPv4 processed packets

targets.query: SELECT mean("delta")  / 60 FROM "lwaftr.lwaftr.statistics.0.in-ipv4-packets" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval) fill(linear)
SELECT mean("delta")  /60 FROM "lwaftr.lwaftr.statistics.0.out-ipv4-packets" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval) fill(linear)
SELECT mean("delta")  / 60 FROM "lwaftr.lwaftr.statistics.0.in-ipv6-packets" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval) fill(linear)
SELECT mean("delta")  / 60 FROM "lwaftr.lwaftr.statistics.0.out-ipv6-packets" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval) fill(linear)
